things such as,

00:17:08.450 --> 00:17:13.070
in this case, it's dishwasher
detergent. The two-liter soda

00:17:13.070 --> 00:17:17.690
bottles and so on are this.
High-density polyethylene, that's

00:17:17.690 --> 00:17:21.930
this one here.
The next one, V,

00:17:21.930 --> 00:17:25.810
is the reaction I showed at the
beginning of the lecture,

00:17:25.810 --> 00:17:29.680
polyvinyl chloride. The fourth one
is low density polyethylene,

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:33.550
which is the stretch and seal and so
on. And, I want you to note that

00:17:33.550 --> 00:17:37.430
all of these have names associated
with them. And,

00:17:37.430 --> 00:17:41.300
these are inventions.
All of these materials that I'm

