00:18:13.730 --> 00:18:17.860
It was polystyrene. He wrote
extensively on it,

00:18:17.860 --> 00:18:36.453
and eventually won the Nobel Prize
for it.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:26.230
Technically, Simon isolated
polystyrene in 1839.

